{"tid":2494502,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"三缸居然比Civic Type R還要快！","createTime":"2021-04-18T15:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:40:39.000Z","uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4299d281cf26f07e6f69e8beda9ed1c6a77b744e","tid":2494502,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"三缸小鴨居然比Civic Type R還要快！TOYOTA GR Yaris非官方紐柏林單圈成績出爐！<br />\n<br />\n堪稱是最強暴力小鴨的TOYOTA GR Yaris從2020年東京車展登場以來，就一直受到台灣車迷的熱烈關注，總代理和泰汽車也終於在上週發佈新車預售訊息，雖然預售價高達了185萬、不過30輛配額卻是瞬間搶訂一空，甚至外傳接單已經達到破300張的盛況！<br />\n值此新車在台展開接單之際，GR Yaris征戰紐柏林北環賽道的非官方單圈成績也正巧出爐，沒想到三缸引擎的暴力小鴨居然比性能鋼砲代名詞HONDA Civic Type R還要更快？<br />\n<br />\n這邊要聲明的是，這次GR Yaris在綠色地獄的8:14.93單圈成績並不是由官方所發布，而是由德國媒體sport auto自行進行的測試，雖然成績是由媒體所發布，但測試車手Christian Gebhardt其實大有來頭，不但本身就是賽車手出身而且還曾三度奪下紐柏林24耐的分組冠軍，專業度無庸置疑。<br />\n<br />\n至於這次測試的主角GR Yaris，雖然是Gazoo Racing總結賽事經驗所操刀打造的賽道機器，不過這個賽道經驗其實是源自於WRC拉力賽場而非紐柏林北環這種場地賽事，再加上還有230km/h的電子限速的枷鎖在，這次能夠跑出8分15秒內的成績真的相當不容易，而且單圈居然還比sport auto此前測試、動力更強的BMW 1M Coupe（8:15）還有Civic Type R FK2（8:15）要更快一點，從這點就可以看到Gazoo Racing的功力所在！<br />\n<br />\n雖然GR Yaris的1.6L渦輪增壓三缸心臟＋iMT 6速手排動力組合「只有」261ps/36.7kgm的輸出表現，但在車體用上大量鋁合金跟碳纖維等輕量化部件的加持下，0~100km/h加速也有5.5秒的不俗水準；而GR Yaris能以小搏大的關鍵其實就在於底盤設定，底盤不是沿用標準版Yaris的GA-B模組化平台，而是採用前GA-B＋後GA-C的寬體設定，還搭載了具備Torsen中央差速器的GR-Four四輪傳動系統，更別提還有Gazoo Racing操刀的賽道化懸吊，這些都造就了GR Yaris出眾的操控本質。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JdeptmXnSfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJdeptmXnSfo&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=19188507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JdeptmXnSfo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.yahoo.com/autos/%E4%B8%89%E7%BC%B8%E5%B0%8F%E9%B4%A8%E5%B1%85%E7%84%B6%E6%AF%94civic-type-r%E9%82%84%E8%A6%81%E5%BF%AB-toyota-gr-060617619.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.yahoo.com%2Fautos%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25B4%25A8%25E5%25B1%2585%25E7%2584%25B6%25E6%25AF%2594civic-type-r%25E9%2582%2584%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%25BF%25AB-toyota-gr-060617619.html&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=60d93374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.yahoo.com/autos/%E4%B8%89%E7%BC%B8%E5%B0%8F%E9%B4%A8%E5%B1%85%E7%84%B6%E6%AF%94civic-type-r%E9%82%84%E8%A6%81%E5%BF%AB-toyota-gr-060617619.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a1a869f88f74b43a368e3c979efaf666078fefd","tid":2494502,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"讓一缸都抽赢你<br />\n唔知邊個打邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f197d67bc74920791213a47938de50f99f9ec503","tid":2494502,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a1a869f88f74b43a368e3c979efaf666078fefd","tid":2494502,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"讓一缸都抽赢你<br />\n唔知邊個打邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"揪"},{"pid":"c7dfd1bd7dd17beab92cee7d25d52279b07bd0ee","tid":2494502,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"都係買本田<br />\n吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23768d94288c9ba150e5c4b7f433120c0615c777","tid":2494502,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7dfd1bd7dd17beab92cee7d25d52279b07bd0ee","tid":2494502,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"都係買本田<br />\n吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"本田我都有 幾好㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdfb6a43f4a70a3b119d566bc60e47f6c001250","tid":2494502,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23768d94288c9ba150e5c4b7f433120c0615c777","tid":2494502,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7dfd1